  "_integrationTestNotes": "Integration tests should verify: (1) Activity_1nvtpnt (Store information and get customer info) calls real CRM API and returns actual customer data including claim frequency; (2) Activity_0iv8gg2 (DMN - fraud rating confidence 'determine-fraud-rating-1dmmwcu') evaluates real rules — COLLECT hit policy, inputs: customer_claim_frequency, vendor_claim_frequency, disputeDetails.disputeAmount.amount. DMN must be deployed: determine_fraud_rating_confidence.dmn; (3) Activity_1ys0vez (Get vendor info) calls real vendor API and returns vendor claim frequency; (4) Activity_1pqdlzs (Initiate credit and clawback action) calls real payment system. Key flow: after Activity_1ys0vez, inner sub-process hits event-based gateway (Gateway_1p7bkh1) — must publish EITHER dispute_process_refund_approved OR dispute_process_refund_declined (correlationKey=disputeDetails.disputeId) to unblock. Taking 'vendor declined' path (dispute_process_refund_declined) throws escalation directly to Activity_0ynau00 (bypasses DMN). Taking 'refund_approved' or timer path goes through DMN. Note: decide_on_fraud_case.form must be deployed."
